  ID: MalteseSoldier
  Name: Lorenzo, Maltese mason
  Icon: {fileID: 409668665, guid: 4147f2bc6fccc974f937adc9cd1a5700, type: 3}
  Description: "He spent twenty years cutting limestone for other men\u2019s fortifications,
    and never finished repairing his own leaking roof. He has a daughter who brings
    him water every afternoon and thinks he is invincible because \u201Cstone protects
    stone.\u201D Now a cannon strike has driven rock fragments deep into his abdomen
    \u2014 the wall he built is killing him\n\nTreatment: The forceps can extract
    only the largest fragments; the deeper ones stay. Bleeding is internal and unstoppable.\n\nRequires:
    1 Bandage"
